  integrationTestResults: "FIX 4.4 ingestion: 99.7% message delivery (29,700 of 29,800 trades over 3 days), average latency 1.3s, max latency 2.8s (during batch window). Okta SSO: SAML 2.0 authentication successful, SCIM user provisioning/deprovisioning functional with <30s propagation. Bloomberg B-PIPE: tested with simulator — adapter recognized FIX tag mapping correctly. Splunk forwarding: JSON log output validated, parsing rules confirmed.",
